		<label>charge pistol</label>
		<description>This high-tech, self-loading pistol uses pulse-charge technology to channel unstable energy into each shot. The charged energy is released on impact, delivering superior damage and armor penetration. Its compact size and reliability make it an ideal backup weapon in high-tech combat.</description>
